                        | The radio web component from the 
                        a(href='https://github.com/material-components/material-components-web-components/tree/master/packages/radio', target='blank') Material Web Components Catalog
                        | have also been utilized in this specific case to add true Material Design radio buttons to this theme.
                    p.mb-4
                        | Similar to the checkboxes above, these radio buttons are larger than most browser defaults. The web component supports unchecked, checked, and disabled states are all supported.

                    +demo({
                        id: 'materialRadio'
                    })
                        +slot('demo')
