                        a(href='https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.2/forms/checks-radios/#checks', target='_blank') Bootstrap's checks &amp; radios documentation
                        | page.

                    +demo({
                        id: 'bootstrapCheckbox'
                    })
                        +slot('demo')
